room_title: Escape room "The Sacrifice" by The Final Door in Columbia
review: Had an awesome time! We did Sacrifice and came so close to escaping! Will definitely go back. The staff were all very friendly and made the experience a great one.

room_title: Escape room "The Sacrifice" by The Final Door in Columbia
review: I have done Sacrifice and Blackout and both have been amazing experiences. A lot of fun to get a few friends together, or get paired up with some strangers, for an hour of finding clues and solving puzzles with the hopes of finishing in time. Looking forward to trying the other rooms they offer.
